    'fc_opportunities_what_title' => 'What It Is',
    'fc_opportunities_what_desc' => 'A sortable, filterable table of every tactical event in your selected window (default: next 7 days). Rows show the EVE timer, a live countdown, the op type (hostile / defense / auto-detected timer), the structure and system, severity, owner / attacker, and how many form-up broadcasts have already been scheduled for the op. Per-event corporation and role visibility from Structure Manager is honored; you only see ops you are entitled to act on.',
    'fc_opportunities_workflow_title' => 'The Action Buttons',
    'fc_opportunities_workflow_desc' => 'Every row has up to three action buttons. <ul><li><strong>📤 Form-up</strong> (primary): opens the <em>Send Broadcast</em> form pre-filled with urgent "forming up NOW" copy + PREPING embed type. Use when the fleet is staging right now and you want to send the broadcast immediately.</li><li><strong>🕒 Schedule</strong>: opens the <em>Scheduled Broadcast</em> form pre-filled for a future formup time. Default scheduled time = timer minus your configured form-up lead time (5-720 min, Settings &gt; Structure Timers). Use when the timer is hours or days away. The resulting scheduled ping is correlated to the op so the "📡 N scheduled" badge counts it.</li><li><strong>ℹ️ Details</strong>: deep-links to the source plugin (Structure Manager for timers, Mining Manager for extractions). Use when you want full context — ore composition, fuel curve, timer history.</li></ul>',
